<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Dec1938"><font color="red">8 December 1938</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of December 6th, which evidently crossed mine of the same date and answers one of your questions. I have been considering &hellip; how soon &hellip; send Mr Joyce an advance copy of his book &hellip; by February 2nd &hellip; What is really urgent now &hellip; is that I should have back the rest of the galley proofs &hellip; page proofs should be sent for press quickly </div>
